content: High Voltage Battery May Short Circuit

Our Next Energy is recalling certain Aries LFP battery packs sold for use in commercial trucks, with part numbers 10108 and 1633.  The battery pack may be improperly sealed and allow liquid to enter the battery.Liquid intrusion into a battery pack can cause a loss of electrical isolation or short circuit, increasing the risk of a fire or shock hazard.

Number of Units Affected: 455.0"
